{"tid":336524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求解脫 屋企人超白痴","createTime":"2017-07-26T13:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T02:51:02.000Z","uid":20115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9915f478659d9085f7e4509d8826201e263e36c8","tid":336524,"uid":20115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"成日係唔適當既時候講埋d令你難堪既野<br />\n例如 食雞唔食雞皮 日常佢地都知 都話食雞皮無益<br />\n但出到去食飯 同叔伯食 佢地就大大聲聲係到講做咩唔食雞皮 浪費食物 係到大仁大意 番到去話唔知你平時唔食開<br />\n<br />\n然後平時係屋企仲有d白痴行為 個港女係大聽同房既人講野 然後人地係房答番佢 佢就話 你係房講野我會聽到咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n然後比人話咁你又要係聽同我講 之後個港女就話 你以後唔洗同我講野 <br />\n房同聽冇咩特別設計 房門開住 <br />\n真係白痴到難以同佢地生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de29380e5a033ec16033f758451c4218d229901","tid":336524,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"廳"},{"pid":"ed5991545351096b7f8e56f12312a052718e4587","tid":336524,"uid":130952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"學好啲中文先同你屋企人嘈"},{"pid":"dac03efba0a4496ef94ef93c9442428991d40547","tid":336524,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6717723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6717723&d=1K44EpHTQQrBuQJGfAxDoZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a115c934\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6717723</a>"}]}